title: Steve Aoki Album
description: Wonderland is the debut studio album by American DJ and producer Steve Aoki, released on January 10, 2012 through Ultra and Dim Mak Records. The remix album was released five months later on June 10, 2012. It features remixes by various electronic artists. Every song from the album was released as a single with its own remixes (except for "Dangerous" and "Livin' My Love").
